question.value:
488 participants (244 Black, 244 White) will be recruited through the Prolific.ac platform, which allows filtering by demographics.

Eligibility criteria:

* must have selected Black or White for simplified ethnicity on the Prolific.ac platform;
* must have selected UK nationality on the Prolific.ac platform;
* must be based in the London area, as this is where we sampled our stimuli from.

Participants will receive £1.56 and the experiment should take no more than 10 minutes. This is equivalent to £9.30 per hour, which is the Real Living Wage in Scotland as of November 2019.

